-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-07/universal-vision-august-sales-rise-19-69-table-3218-tt.html
UNIVERSAL VISION said unconsolidated sales
in August rose 19.69% to NT$70,702,000 from NT$59,073,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  8/2011           8/2010
Sales             70,702           59,073    
YOY%              19.69%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            539,048          435,987    
YOY%              23.64% 
=================================================================
 